Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.74,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Waaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.04,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,I see that today is the same old routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:17.49,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,You're always acting peculiar Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.74,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,But! But! But!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.64,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,You're not bothered by any of this Tsubasa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:26.00,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Being held in this place for who knows how long and we can't see anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.50,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Well, even if you put it that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.92,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Considering the damage done to the moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.90,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,and until they've had time to deal with all the events surrounding that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:37.77,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,acting as if we've gone missing in order to safeguard against the unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.35,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,was the decision that the Commander and everyone came to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:40.51,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,And furthermore…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:42.18,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I knooow…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:46.35,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,It's also to make sure Miku doesn't get \Nput in any danger… right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:47.02,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.02,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Waaaah! I want to see Mikuuuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.07,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,There's no doubt she's sleepless without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:57.91,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,When it comes to Kohinata you certainly become more self-aware than usual, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:02.14,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I know the only thing I'm useful for is warming up the cold futon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:05.50,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,but since I've disappeared I know she must be really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.74,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,And I haven't even given back the money I owe her yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:08.49,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Oh geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.42,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Not to mention if we leave here and I show up like, “Hey, I was okay all along!”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:13.69,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,When she's hears that she'll definitely get upset…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.19,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Saying things like “Why didn't you call and tell me earlier?!”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:18.76,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,No matter how I look at it, an angry Miku is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:21.95,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I mean, even when we eat meals together she just won't talk to me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.79,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,But then, even if I stay here forever \Nit would be really boring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:27.30,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Staving off boredom and having Miku mad at me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:29.17,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I'm not experienced enough to deal with either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:32.27,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Stuck here till we get out, I can leave and smile like that's a good excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.28,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,But that won't be the end because dfhoudhfoawewoiejwsddofushfoh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.62,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tachibana….hey Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:36.11,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:41.51,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Is the one you're worried about Kohinata? Or is it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.83,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Well of course that's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.04,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.96,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.96,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.96,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75\bord0}of the moon fragment part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.96,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75}of the moon fragment part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:55.13,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,The way things worked out I ended up joining hands with them, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:57.63,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,I can't laugh and smile like they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.28,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,No, I can't allow myself to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:05.14,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,From here on, I can't just ignore all the wrongdoings I committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.81,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,If I don't then…I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.81,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's wrong Chris-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:07.64,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.48,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\an8}You've been so quiet all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.56,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I got it! You're hungry aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.53,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I know, I know that feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.24,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,When you feel seriously empty inside and just wanna chow down, talking is such a paaaain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.99,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,So what do you wanna do? Order a pizza or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:25.91,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,I was just looking at a flyer in the newspaper earlier for this delicious, calorie-filled…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.41,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,You're so annoying! A bona fide idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:32.75,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,C-Chris is so hungry she's turned into a bully!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.51,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Just shut up! I'm trying to sort things out with myself, so be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:42.01,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Even just for a moment give me some peace and quieeeet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:47.52,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.51,0:02:47.52,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:47.52,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75}of the moon fragment part 3
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.51,0:02:47.52,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75\bord0}of the moon fragment part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.41,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,All the sins I've committed up until yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:52.65,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,aren't something I can atone for easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.53,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Because I understand that I won't try to escape anymore.{It's because I understand that, that I won't try to escape anymore.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.19,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,That's right, peace… isn't something that…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:06.35,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Since there's already a big…. wall right in the center... of my…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.45,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.15,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Now it's her, why's she only being silent and staring so intently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:19.30,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,W-what is it? Instead of just sitting there, how about you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.30,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,To live means to be combat-ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:28.06,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Forget it! Don't say anything to me! I'm begging you, just stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.56,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Now now, don't say that…Yukine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:35.56,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Isn't there a single normal person in this plaaaace?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.56,0:03:40.57,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:40.57,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
