Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:40.57,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75}of the moon fragment part 4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:47.16,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,And with that, I'll introduce her once again: Yukine Chris-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.76,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,As the user of the second relic, Ichaival, she'll be a reliable comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.17,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,T-Thanks. N-nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:04:00.59,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,And also today, the restriction on the 3 user's actions will be lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.01,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Master, in other words you mean…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:06.10,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,That's right! You can all return to your daily lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.10,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Hooray! I can finally see Mikuuuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.05,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,We've also prepared a residence for Chris-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.67,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,You can live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.20,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,A p-place for me? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:21.99,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Of course! I guarantee you freedom and privacy at all times other than when you're on a mission as a user.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.25,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Yukine! I've got a duplicate key!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.91,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,I can come over to play anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.87,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:38.34,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,And I've got my copy and…can you believe it, Miku's too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.46,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO PRIVACY OR FREEDOM ANYWHERE IN THIS!!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.13,0:04:47.14,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:47.14,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur2}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.13,0:04:47.14,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75\bord0}of the moon fragment part 5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:47.14,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur2}of the moon fragment part 5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.89,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,This is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.14,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,The Noise emergence alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:59.36,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Our actions aren't restricted anymore, so from here on out I will fulfill my duty as a sentinel to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.10,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Let's go out there together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.19,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.53,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,I can't go out there and fight while holding hands with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.16,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,But that's our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.04,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Even so! I-it doesn't mean we're best friends all of a sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.14,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Why are you two wasting time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.79,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Do that sort of thing at your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.13,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,You're saying do THIS at home?!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.67,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.67,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.67,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75\bord0}of the moon fragment part 6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.67,Moon,Chris,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75}of the moon fragment part 6
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.81,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Sorry… there were a lot of secrets I had to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:37.64,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Yet again... I couldn't tell you the truth Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hibiki….Hibiki….
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.47,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Haha, I knew it, you must've been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.47,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hibiki…Hibiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.28,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Haha… that kind of hurts a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:45.92,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hibiki…Hibiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.28,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Uh, maybe more than just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.34,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hibiki Hibiki Hibiki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.39,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Uh, Miku? Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.07,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}HibikiHibikiHibiki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:54.55,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.48,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}HibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibiki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.64,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Stop it! Quit it! Stop it! Quit it! Stop it! Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:58.79,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,{\an8}HibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibikiHibiki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:58.79,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,AH! UWAAH!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.79,0:06:03.80,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75\bord0}of the moon fragment part 7
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:03.80,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,554)\blur1.75}of the moon fragment part 7
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.79,0:06:03.80,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75\bord0}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:03.80,Moon,Hibiki,0,0,0,,{\pos(822,200)\blur1.75}Roughly 2 weeks after the destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:14.18,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm really sorry. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.68,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you. So I won't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.75,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm not letting go until I've forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.90,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.93,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Ah, good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.82,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Kids of the modern generation are all like this, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.77,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Certainly this is something they'd be best going off to do at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:35.91,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Again, you say do THIS this at home?! What's with YOU people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:41.75,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 1
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.75,0:06:41.75,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:45.09,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there's something I've been meaning to ask about for awhile now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:49.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,The whole “singing while fighting” situation, how exactly does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:51.72,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Hm, well the best way to put it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.97,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,The Symphogear works just like a karaoke machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.56,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Karaoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.65,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Yeah! I don't really get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:04.23,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,But when the music starts playing from the Symphogear, the lyrics just kind of well up from inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.87,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Lyrics… from inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.11,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's pretty much what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:15.76,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,The lyrics are also born straight from the user's imagination, at least Miss Sakurai said as much once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:22.50,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Think about it. Lyrics like “Question? Stupid question! Impulse inspire” and such are perfectly fitting for Yukine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.37,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.92,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,There's even stuff like “Rasetsu install” too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:30.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Stop it Hibiki, don't say things that will “gouge out wounds.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.55,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,You jerks…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.66,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Hmph, your personality is always so untamed Yukine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:42.06,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute! You're the last person I want to hear that from!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.90,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,My songs may clearly show my honest personality, but yours are just the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:50.44,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,If that's what you call a “personality,” it's on a level even a psychiatrist would run away from!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:55.45,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 2
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.44,0:07:55.45,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.66,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Relocating along with the Lydian Music Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.88,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Are also new student dorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.37,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,And with that! Let's start customizing the bunk beds right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:09.62,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It was the same with our old dorm, but you always put a lot of effort into this part Hibiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:14.46,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,If we sleep together on the top bed, the bottom bed can be conveniently used as storage space!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.18,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's our own consolidated storage technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:23.85,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,That being said… with a room this wide, we could get by without having to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Though… personally, I don't see any reason to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:36.15,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Afterall, Miku is my sunshine! Next to you is the place I can sleep the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Hibiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:45.96,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,My best friend who calls me her sunshine doesn't realize that she's actually the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.46,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,So let's sleep together again tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:52.28,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,But sometimes she's so radiant it's just too overwhelming!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.09,0:08:58.10,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:58.10,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.60,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,I had no idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.98,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,The Symphogear users of Div 2 get an allowance…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.48,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,That idiot definitely…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.31,Default,Hibiki,0,0,0,,Rice! And rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.32,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Seems the type to spend all of her money on foodstuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.33,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,And on the other hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:15.49,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,To live means to be combat-ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:21.49,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,She leaves the image of buying an endless supply of bikes to jump off of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.83,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,But this is just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:24.66,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,{\an8}To live means to be combat-ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:28.83,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Now… I wonder what should I do with mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.90,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,And so… you'll be accompanying me shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.05,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,But why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.96,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Because those two won't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.71,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Why? Are you looking for action movies \Nto get battle plans from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.60,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.47,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Eh… a Buddhist altar store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.64,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Hehe… I came to buy the coolest altar they've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:50.36,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,This is… unexpected, or rather…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.92,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,You've got more of a grim hobby than I expected…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.38,0:09:59.36,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:59.36,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.49,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.04,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Making you carry all the heavy luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.62,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,But thanks to you, I'm all settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.96,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,To be frank, I didn't think I'd have to act as your delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:14.38,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,So, what are you planning by buying this altar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:19.89,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Without it this is a house that only I come home to, and I don't want to feel like I left out my Papa and Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:24.23,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,Though on the way here from the alter store,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:28.24,Default,Genjuurou,0,0,0,,we must've been questioned by the police at least 7 seven times.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.40,0:10:34.40,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:34.40,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.57,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Someday… I want to sing with the world as my stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.07,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,But, I am a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.77,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Until the day we end the calamity of the Noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:48.58,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,my fate is to stand on the battlefield as a sentinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:52.34,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Tsubasa-san! There's trouble, Tsubasa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.80,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Ogawa-san! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.97,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Well… about that request for your appearance on a quiz variety show
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.63,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,What should we do, Tsubasa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:03.30,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Potentially, we could use it to promote your new single…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:08.06,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,A q-q-quiz?! W-what exactly are they asking me to do for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.31,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Well, naturally, they're wondering if you'll answer some quiz questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.15,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:12.98,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:17.98,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Sung of even in the Man'yōshū, these were established in defense of Kyushu's coast…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.82,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Sentinels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.83,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Wow, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:24.66,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Not at all, this is just knowledge one needs in everyday life…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.46,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 6
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.46,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 6
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.96,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm going to keep the questions coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.02,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,I welcome the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.79,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:40.04,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,This was a well-known motto of the Nagaoka domain's leader and commander-in-chief
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.59,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,of WW2's Combined Fleet, Yamamoto Isoroku…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.34,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,To live means to be combat-ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.45,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:50.60,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Holding the meaning of “inconsistency” what exactly is a contradiction, a “shield” that is capable of reflecting anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.85,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,It's a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:54.35,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Wrong! The correct answer was long spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.95,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Gah, so that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.86,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,You're unexpectedly adept at this, I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.81,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,It seems somehow it's started to bloom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:05.03,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,this hidden inner talent of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:09.75,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go change your schedule so we'll be able to accept the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.08,Default,Tsubasa,0,0,0,,Huh? W-wait, Ogawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:18.71,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,Making sure Tsubasa-san's songs reach a large number of people is my job afterall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.08,Default,Ogawa,0,0,0,,This seems like it'll be an excellent opportunity!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.72,0:12:27.72,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75\bord0}Shortly before the start of G part 7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:27.72,G,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,498.8)\blur1.75}Shortly before the start of G part 7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.48,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Good mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.15,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Sorry for being so noisy first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.32,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,But being noisy is fitting for a family of musicians,\N don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.50,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm off to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:51.38,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,To be honest…I'm not used to it yet, and it's a noisy place…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:57.25,Default,Chris,0,0,0,,But since I'm Papa and Mama's daughter, I guess I don't dislike it when it's noisy.
